53082::$$$message_0457_0000_0000$$$::I can't do anything about the fact that I forgot. I'll ask her to let it slide.::
53083::$$$message_0457_0001_0000$$$::"Oh, sorry. I ran into someone unexpected today, so I forgot. I'll be careful next time, so would you let this slide?"[lr]::
53084::$$$message_0457_0001_0001$$$::I bow in apology.::
53085::$$$message_0457_0002_0000$$$::"...Oh, really? You're going to gloss over this with a few words. I thought you were different from Kiritsugu, but you're really just the same."[lr]::
53086::$$$message_0457_0002_0001$$$::"Huh? Illya?"::
53087::$$$message_0457_0003_0000$$$::"Fine. It's more fun for me that way. I'll turn you into my plaything, just like I planned."[lr]::
53088::$$$message_0457_0003_0001$$$::"...!?"[lr]::
53089::$$$message_0457_0003_0002$$$::I feel a terrible chill.[lr]::
53090::$$$message_0457_0003_0003$$$::Illya's eyes give off the same animosity they had the night we first met.::
53091::$$$message_0457_0004_0000$$$::"Bye then, big brother. I'll let you off for today, but you'd better be careful the next time we meet."[lr]::
53092::$$$message_0457_0004_0001$$$::She runs away without a second thought.[lr]::
53093::$$$message_0457_0004_0002$$$::"Wai[line2]Illya!"::
53094::$$$message_0457_0005_0000$$$::I try to folllow her, but I lose sight of her before I can catch up.::
53095::$$$message_0457_0006_0000$$$::"...I wonder if I made her mad."[lr]::
53096::$$$message_0457_0006_0001$$$::That was a failure.[lr]::
53097::$$$message_0457_0006_0002$$$::I should've apologized to Illya, no doubt about it.::
53098::$$$message_0457_0007_0000$$$::"(Sigh) I'd better think of something before I see her again."[lr]::
53099::$$$message_0457_0007_0001$$$::I don't want things to break down between us.[lr]::
53100::$$$message_0457_0007_0002$$$::I'll think of a way to cheer her up, and make it up to her for breaking my promise.::

